  "response": "Ryan Gosling is recognized not only for his acting but also for his singing abilities. He showcased his musical talent in films like \"La La Land,\" where he performed several songs and received praise for his vocal performance. His work in the film contributed to a positive reception of his singing skills. Additionally, he has been involved in musical projects outside of acting, such as his band, Dead Man's Bones. Many fans and critics appreciate his unique style and versatility as a singer. Overall, while opinions on singing ability can be subjective, Gosling is generally regarded as a good singer.",
